			div(class="section no-pad-bot" id="index-banner")
				div(class="container")
				<br> <br>
				h1(class="header center black-text titleIndex strech") SWAPP!
				div(class="row center")
					h5(class="header col s12 light") A useful app to swap what you're not using anymore. If you both swapped, you get a match!
				div(class="row center")
					a(href="#linkScroll" id="download-button" class="btn-large waves-effect waves-light orange smoothScroll")
